author: @lindezagrey4982
text: Hey there, why not use parameterized queries? e.g. "Select comment from parent_reply where comment_id = ?" and then call c. execute(sql, args) That's not only best practice to prevent sql injection but should also boost performance especially on Insert statements.  Keep up your good work!
